The app doesn't function as advertised.

00:12:46.840 --> 00:12:50.380
It doesn't do what the
developer says it does.

00:12:50.380 --> 00:12:52.380
So we reject it.

00:12:52.440 --> 00:12:54.680
We say, "You said it did this,
it does this.

00:12:54.680 --> 00:12:56.940
Change your description
or change your app,

00:12:56.940 --> 00:13:00.120
