told us it did." The second

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:02.560
reason is use of private APIs.

00:13:02.560 --> 00:13:04.900
We're very clear on this.

00:13:04.900 --> 00:13:06.680
Developers can't use private APIs.

00:13:06.680 --> 00:13:07.810
Why not?

00:13:08.230 --> 00:13:11.540
Because when we change the OS,
those private APIs are not

00:13:11.540 --> 00:13:14.420
