00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:24.560
So you can't use private APIs.

00:13:24.560 --> 00:13:26.820
And developers that use private APIs,
of course,

00:13:26.820 --> 00:13:28.460
know exactly what they're doing.

00:13:29.240 --> 00:13:31.830
So...

00:13:32.210 --> 00:13:36.180
And the third reason we reject apps,
the third most frequent reason,

00:13:36.180 --> 00:13:37.550
they crash.

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:40.700
So I think if you were in our shoes,
you would be rejecting these

00:13:40.700 --> 00:13:43.040
